NI 45-106 and shall only include those persons who may participate in an “Employee Benefit Plan” as set forth
in Rule 405 of the U.S. Securities Act;

“Eligible Person” means, from time to time, a full-time or part-time employee
of the Company or of a related entity of the Company, including any officer of the Company, a Consultant of the Company or of a
